@prefix : <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix bytestar: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core>
  a owl:Ontology ;
  owl:versionInfo "0.1.0" ;
  rdfs:label "ByteStar Core Ontology" ;
  rdfs:comment "Foundational classes, properties, and invariants for Byte* ecosystem." .

### Core classes
System, Subsystem, ByteActor, ByteFlow, ByteEthos, Fabricator, CPUFabricator, GPUFabricator,
Crystal, Envelope, Kernel, KernelSet, Pattern, PatternRegistry, Graph, Workflow, Admission, Acceptance, Rejection,
Receipt, LedgerSegment, Validator, Observer, RingBuffer, Pulse, DeterminismStamp, MPHFTable, LOUDSTrie, XORFilter, Bitset
  a owl:Class .

### Subsystem taxonomy
ByteActor rdfs:subClassOf Subsystem .
ByteFlow  rdfs:subClassOf Subsystem .
ByteEthos rdfs:subClassOf Subsystem .
CPUFabricator rdfs:subClassOf Fabricator .
GPUFabricator rdfs:subClassOf Fabricator .

### Doctrine (8/8) — datatype constraints
:hasTickCost a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain Kernel ; rdfs:range xsd:integer .
:hasHopCount a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain Workflow ; rdfs:range xsd:integer .

# Tick ≤ 8 for all kernels
Kernel rdfs:subClassOf [
  a owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty :hasTickCost ;
  owl:allValuesFrom [ a rdfs:Datatype ;
    owl:onDatatype xsd:integer ;
    owl:withRestrictions ( [ xsd:minInclusive "0"^^xsd:integer ]
                            [ xsd:maxInclusive "8"^^xsd:integer ] ) ] ] .

# Hop ≤ 8 for all workflows that run hot
Workflow rdfs:subClassOf [
  a owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty :hasHopCount ;
  owl:allValuesFrom [ a rdfs:Datatype ;
    owl:onDatatype xsd:integer ;
    owl:withRestrictions ( [ xsd:minInclusive "0"^^xsd:integer ]
                            [ xsd:maxInclusive "8"^^xsd:integer ] ) ] ] .

### Pattern Byte & congruence
:patternByte a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain Crystal ;
  rdfs:range [ a rdfs:Datatype ; owl:onDatatype xsd:unsignedByte ;
               owl:withRestrictions ( [ xsd:minInclusive "0"^^xsd:unsignedByte ]
                                      [ xsd:maxInclusive "255"^^xsd:unsignedByte ] ) ] .

:declaresPattern a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain Crystal ; rdfs:range Pattern .
:congruentWith    a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain Graph   ; rdfs:range Pattern .

### Admission
:hasDecision a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain Admission ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:decidesFor  a owl:ObjectProperty   ; rdfs:domain Admission ; rdfs:range Crystal .
:consumesHotTicks a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain Admission ; rdfs:range xsd:integer .

# Zero-tick rejection
Rejection owl:equivalentClass [ a owl:Class ;
  owl:intersectionOf ( Admission [ a owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty :hasDecision ;
                                   owl:hasValue "false"^^xsd:boolean ] ) ] .
Rejection rdfs:subClassOf [ a owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty :consumesHotTicks ;
                            owl:hasValue "0"^^xsd:integer ] .

Acceptance owl:equivalentClass [ a owl:Class ;
  owl:intersectionOf ( Admission [ a owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty :hasDecision ;
                                   owl:hasValue "true"^^xsd:boolean ] ) ] .

### Determinism & provenance
:deterministic a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain System ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:determinismDigest a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain DeterminismStamp ; rdfs:range xsd:hexBinary .
:hasStamp a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain (System) ; rdfs:range DeterminismStamp .

### L1 residency set
:l1Resident a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain Subsystem ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:l1Holds    a owl:ObjectProperty   ; rdfs:domain ByteActor ;
            rdfs:range [ a owl:Class ; owl:unionOf ( KernelSet MPHFTable Envelope ) ] .

### Execution & queues
:executes a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain ByteActor ; rdfs:range Kernel .
:enqueues a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain ByteFlow  ; rdfs:range Crystal .
:connectsTo a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain RingBuffer ; rdfs:range Subsystem .
:isSPSC a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain RingBuffer ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### Pulse/Observers
:emitsPulse a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain ByteActor ; rdfs:range Pulse .
:observes   a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain Observer  ; rdfs:range Pulse .
:offPath    a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain Observer ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### Crypto/PQC
:PQCKey, :PQCSignature, :PQCOperation a owl:Class .
:verifies a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain Subsystem ; rdfs:range PQCSignature .
:signs    a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain Subsystem ; rdfs:range PQCSignature .
:keygens  a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain Subsystem ; rdfs:range PQCKey .

### Governance
:finalizes a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain ByteEthos ; rdfs:range LedgerSegment .
:approvedBy a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain LedgerSegment ; rdfs:range Validator .
:weight    a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain Validator ; rdfs:range xsd:decimal .
:threshold a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain ByteEthos ; rdfs:range xsd:decimal .

### Annotations for doctrine
ByteActor rdfs:comment "Let-it-crash: no runtime tick guards; hot-path constant-schedule." .